                  <li class="typewrite">Created mounting components for HVAC, electrical, and laboratory instruments.</li>
                  <li class="typewrite">Gathered researcher requirements and developed budget-conscious fixture designs to improve lab usability and setup efficiency.</li>
                </ul>

